{"article_id":"ZwlAkcdjlyWweu2t","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Republican lawmakers spent the last seven years","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"vowing to repeal and replace Obamacare ,","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"and","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"while the House took a first step toward that end Thursday in the narrow passage of the American Health Care Act ,","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"syndicated columnist made an ominous prediction","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"about where health care in this country is heading .","depth":3},{"id":6,"text":"\" Historically speaking we are at the midpoint","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"and we had seven years of Obamacare , changing expectations .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"I would predict","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"that in less than seven years , we will be in a single-payer system , \"","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"he told Fox News host Chris Wallace .","depth":3},{"id":11,"text":"This ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"he said ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"is the \" great irony \" -","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"that","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"despite the electoral losses","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Democrats faced","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"because of the Affordable Care Act","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"and even though the law has largely failed in practice ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Obamacare will still win in the end .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"\" Obamacare failed at every level politically .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"...","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"As you say ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"they lost seats in the House , Senate , governorships .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"Largely because of Obamacare .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"It failed on the ground ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"as was pointed out earlier .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"The insurers are in a dead spiral .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"The Obamacare exchanges are collapsing .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"You 've had these exchanges ... completely disintegrating .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"But the irony is in the end ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Obamacare wins the day","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"because it changed expectations , \"","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"\" Look at the terms of the debate .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"Republicans are not arguing the free market anymore .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"They have sort of accepted the fact","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"that the electorate sees healthcare as not just any commodity .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"It 's not like purchasing a steak or a car .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"It is something","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"people now have a sense","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"that government ought to guarantee . ''","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"Wallace pushed back ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"asking","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"how we are going to get to single-payer","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"and wondering","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"if he was saying","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"the Senate would not pass the repeal and replace plan ?","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Krauthammer said","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"in the short term , the Senate will not accept the House plan","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"but will come up with one of its own .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"While he acknowledged","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"he didn ' t know how that would end up ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"he was certain","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"\" it ' s going to be a rickety arrangement. \"","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"This in turn will negatively affect Republicans at the polls .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"\" It ' s likely that Republicans are going to suffer at the polls .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"And as a result of that ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"if that happens ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"you 're going to get a sea change in opinion","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"and then there ' s only two ways to go :","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"to a radically individualist system","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"where the market rules","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"or single-payer .","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"And the country is not going to go back to radical individualist , \"","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"he said .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":133,"left":72,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":70,"right":71,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":70,"left":68,"right":69,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":76,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":75,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":73,"right":74,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":73,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":131,"left":84,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":78,"right":83,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":77,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":77,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":82,"right":19,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":82,"left":14,"right":81,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":81,"left":80,"right":18,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":80,"left":79,"right":17,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":98,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"le